          <h1>Eeny, Meeny, Miny, Moe</h1>
          <p>
            Decision Wizard is a web app that helps you make decisions
            collaboratively by making polls.<br> Make a poll question, add a few
            options to choose from, and we'll generate a link that you can send
            out to your friends. You'll get notified as your friends complete
            the poll, and we'll calculate the winning choice based on everyone's
            votes.<span class="asterix">*</span>
          </p>
          <p class="italics"><span>*</span>the final, final decision will still be determined by a round-robin rock-paper-scissors tournament, winner-takes-all eeny meeny miny moe double-elimation in the event of a tie.</p>
